<br>
Modal Damage Output Primary Hand = [(2*DMG + Damage Bonus)/Delay]*[1<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <br>
<br>
( Note: the factor of 10 at the end converts Delay to Seconds)<br>
<br>
Modal Damage Output Secondary Hand = [(2*DMG)/Delay]*[1<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> *[(Level + Dual Wield Skill)/100)]<br>
<br>
(Note: the last part of the formula is the success chance for Dual Wield, not including any AA abilities)<br>
<br>
<br>
You cannot Double Attack with the secondary hand until your Double Attack skill reaches 150. Therefore, to account for Double Attack you must:<br>
<br>
1. Multiply the DPS of your primary hand by 1 + [(Level + Double Attack Skill)/50<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 0] --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/alien.gif ALT="0]"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
2. If Double Attack skill is 150+, do the same for the secondary hand; otherwise don't.<br>
<br>
<br>
To account for haste:<br>
<br>
1. Find (or measure for yourself) your total haste% in terms of increased number of attacks.<br>
<br>
2. Multiply your total damage output by 1 + haste%  (e.g. multiply by 1.22 for Silver Chitin Handwraps)<br>
<br>
<br>
Now you have a theoretical number which you probably won't reach. If you want a more accurate predictor of actual damage, therre are 2 more things to look at:<br>
<br>
1. Hit%: Analyze your logfile to determine the percentage of hits which cause damage against your typical opponents. Factor that in.<br>
<br>
2. Average Damage: Analyze your logfiles to determine how close Modal Damage is to your actual Average Damage. This will vary according to your STR, +ATK Buffs, the Damage Mitigation AC of your opponent, etc. Adjust your DPS prediction appropriately.<br>
<br>
<br>
How is that? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=predatoryinstinct>Predatory Instinct</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/22/03 11:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2804.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: DPS</span><hr size=1> Exactly what I was looking for Daleb<br>
